title: KISS_NASHIVILLE_95_live
description:
KISS Nashville, Tennessee 1995

Date: 95-07-09
Venue: Nashville Convention Center

Recording: AUD
Quality: 8(+)
Menu: NO
Extras: None
The display footage is excellent, showing most of the cool exhibits.
Clinic and Q&A footage is a tri-pod in the back. 
Unplugged gig is also a tri-pod that's set on a fairly straight wide-angle zoom. 
Picture quality is a little dark and lacking in color. Audio is very good.
